What is database...

A database is the collection of data that can be easily accessed, managed and update, retrival

why we use database>>>>
1) To store large amounts of data
2) to retrieve data quickly and accurately
3) To update and delete the data as needed
4) to ensure data security etc


Types of Databases:
1) Relational Databases(RDBMS)..Relational Database management System
   -> Data is stored in tables (rows and columns)
    -> MYSQL, PostgreSQL, Oracle

2) NoSql Databases- used for unstructured data...document (jSON)

{
    name: "venkat",
    address: "123 T Nager"
}
  
   